Use posix_spawn for ProxyCommand and ProxyUseFdpass helpers. These children
immediately execute a shell, so POSIX's atomic spawn operation preserves the
native OpenSSH pipe/socketpair descriptor wiring, environment, signal default,
and helper lifecycle without depending on an address-space snapshot.

